OL,3,CFree prom shop opens for young school
OL,4,Cpupils
OL,6,FA free prom shop has opened in Salford
OL,7,Fto make sure everyone has the chance
OL,8,Fto dress to impress on prom night.
OL,10,FThe shop in Walkden is designed to
OL,11,Fmake prom shopping more affordable,
OL,12,Fwith many prom dresses costing more
OL,13,Fthan one hundred pounds.
OL,15,FShop owner Becky Marshall set up the
OL,16,Fshop to reduce the pressure on parents
OL,17,Fto pay large sums for a prom dress, as
OL,18,Fshe wants every pupil to be able to
OL,19,Fcelebrate the landmark moment of
OL,20,Fleaving school.
