OL,4,Cpupils
OL,6,FShe said: "There's no criteria, we
OL,7,Fdon't require parents to be on
OL,8,Fbenefits. We believe that every young
OL,9,Fperson should go to prom."
OL,11,FSchoolgirl Leoni took home a green
OL,12,Fdress from the pop-up shop.
OL,14,FShe said: "It's really heartwarming
OL,15,Fbecause when it gets close to prom
OL,16,Fthere is a pressure to find a dress
OL,17,Ffor hundreds of pounds.
OL,19,F"When I found out about this place I
OL,20,Fwas dead happy and it relieved the
OL,21,Fpressure.
