OL,6,FShe said the feeling of not going
OL,7,Fwould have been "gutting".
OL,9,FProm dresses are often worn for one
OL,10,Fnight, so Becky wants them to be put
OL,11,Fto use for other people, rather than
OL,12,Fbeing left in wardrobes.
OL,14,FBecky said: "The expense is so high at
OL,15,Fthe moment that parents are being put
OL,16,Funder enormous pressure to provide
OL,17,Fsomething that isn't as justifiable as
OL,18,Fit used to be.
