OL,6,F"We would like to take the pressure
OL,7,Foff parents but ensure that no young
OL,8,Fperson misses out on that milestone
OL,9,Fmemory."
OL,11,FThe pop-up is already fully booked for
OL,12,Fweeks, as pupils across the region are
OL,13,Fpreparing for the summer celebration
OL,14,Fand the end of their secondary school
OL,15,Fjourney.
